{"an8.53:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 8.53 ","an8.53:0.2":"6. Gotamivagga ","an8.53:0.3":"Sankhittasutta ","an8.53:1.1":"Ekam samayam bhagava vesaliyam viharati mahavane kutagarasalayam. ","an8.53:1.2":"Atha kho mahapajapati gotami yena bhagava tenupasankami; upasankamitva bhagavantam abhivadetva ekamantam atthasi. Ekamantam thita kho sa mahapajapati gotami bhagavantam etadavoca: ","an8.53:2.1":"“Sadhu me, bhante, bhagava sankhittena dhammam desetu, yamaham bhagavato dhammam sutva eka vupakattha appamatta atapini pahitatta vihareyyan”ti. ","an8.53:2.2":"“Ye kho tvam, gotami, dhamme janeyyasi: ","an8.53:2.3":"‘ime dhamma saragaya samvattanti, no viragaya; ","an8.53:2.4":"samyogaya samvattanti, no visamyogaya; ","an8.53:2.5":"acayaya samvattanti, no apacayaya; ","an8.53:2.6":"mahicchataya samvattanti, no appicchataya; ","an8.53:2.7":"asantutthiya samvattanti, no santutthiya; ","an8.53:2.8":"sanganikaya samvattanti, no pavivekaya; ","an8.53:2.9":"kosajjaya samvattanti, no viriyarambhaya; ","an8.53:2.10":"dubbharataya samvattanti, no subharataya’ti, ","an8.53:2.11":"ekamsena, gotami, dhareyyasi: ","an8.53:2.12":"‘neso dhammo, neso vinayo, netam satthusasanan’ti. ","an8.53:3.1":"Ye ca kho tvam, gotami, dhamme janeyyasi: ","an8.53:3.2":"‘ime dhamma viragaya samvattanti, no saragaya; ","an8.53:3.3":"visamyogaya samvattanti, no samyogaya; ","an8.53:3.4":"apacayaya samvattanti, no acayaya; ","an8.53:3.5":"appicchataya samvattanti, no mahicchataya; ","an8.53:3.6":"santutthiya samvattanti, no asantutthiya; ","an8.53:3.7":"pavivekaya samvattanti, no sanganikaya; ","an8.53:3.8":"viriyarambhaya samvattanti, no kosajjaya; ","an8.53:3.9":"subharataya samvattanti, no dubbharataya’ti, ","an8.53:3.10":"ekamsena, gotami, dhareyyasi: ","an8.53:3.11":"‘eso dhammo, eso vinayo, etam satthusasanan’”ti. ","an8.53:3.12":"Tatiyam. "}